The '''Southern Hills Queen Moocher''' was the head breeder for the largest [[Moocher]] colony in the southern hill. She took her place after suffocating her aging and sterile predecessor, ruling for over thirteen Moocher generations.<ref name="CCW">''[[Coruscant and the Core Worlds]]''</ref>

